<summary>Hardware monitor for CPU, GPU and sensors with an always-on-top widget.</summary>

<description>
  <p>
    CoreX is a hardware monitoring tool for Linux systems. 
    It provides real-time data for the processor (CPU), graphics card (GPU), RAM and system sensors.
  </p>
  <p>
    Features a customizable, always-on-top desktop widget that allows you to keep track 
    of system performance without switching windows.
  </p>
</description>

<keywords>
  <keyword>hardware monitor</keyword>
  <keyword>system monitor</keyword>
  <keyword>sensor</keyword>
  <keyword>sensors</keyword>
  <keyword>cpu</keyword>
  <keyword>gpu</keyword>
  <keyword>widget</keyword>
  <keyword>always-on-top</keyword>
</keywords>

